List all available controller settings:confopts_ph.sh -p list -a Ctrls | more
List all currently available bluetooth controllers:listblue_ph.sh | more
View the current value of controller setting(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Ctrls -g
View the current value of controller setting(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Ctrls -g -r
Set the controller type to PS3:confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Ctrls -o PH_CTRL_TYPE='PS3' -o PH_CTRL_MAP='no' | more
Set the controller type to PS3 with XBOX360 controller emulation:confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Ctrls -o PH_CTRL_TYPE='PS3' -o PH_CTRL_MAP='yes' | more
Set the controller type to PS4:confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Ctrls -o PH_CTRL_TYPE='PS4' -o PH_CTRL_MAP='no' | more
Set the controller type to PS4 with XBOX360 controller emulation:confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Ctrls -o PH_CTRL_TYPE='PS4' -o PH_CTRL_MAP='yes' | more
Set the controller type to XBOX360:confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Ctrls -o PH_CTRL_TYPE='XBOX360' | more
Display help for controller setting(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Ctrls -d
Display help for controller setting(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Ctrls -d -r
Go to Main menu:ph_show_menu Main
Go to Controllers menu:ph_show_menu Controllers
Return to previous screen:return
